title: New Hampshire Gov. Maggie Hassan to challenge Kelly Ayotte for Senate seat
text: New Hampshire Gov. Maggie Hassan (D) on Monday announced that she will challenge incumbent GOP Sen. Kelly Ayotte, ending months of speculation about her Senate ambitions and teeing up what could be one of the marquee Senate races of 2016.
